node.excerpt: 🤔 Missing “key” prop..? but no array..? If you are reading this post, you’ve probably got an error like this where you don’t even have any array.map in your component.  This is an issue with eslint-plugin-react version 7.29.0. To fix the issue, simply down grade eslint-plugin-react to 7.28.0. Reference: https://github.com/yannickcr/eslint-plugin-react/issues/3215

frontmatter.title: Missing "key" prop for element when there is no array
